"<p align=\"center\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:transparent;\"><span style=\" font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">A target showing on a disc means it is vulnerable to capture, the plain side means it is safe)</span><span style=\" font-size:11pt; color:#000000;\"><br />• Each player lays their 2 sets of discs out horizontally in front of them in the following way:</span></p>\n"
